data.description: Now through January 31, 2024, we are offering $12,500 in incentives to be used for closing costs, interest rate buy downs, blinds, refrigerator, fence, etc. This brand-new 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home offers 2,241 square feet of modern living space. Enjoy the open floor plan, seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining. Park your vehicles in the convenient side entry 2-car garage, and explore the vibrant community featuring a lake, sidewalks, and a park/playground. Don't miss out – schedule your viewing today!
